<template>

            <Body style="height: 40vh;" :ProductDetails="product" class="mx-6"/>

import Body from '../Components/Body.vue'
import Footer from '../Components/Footer.vue'


export default {
    name: "Card",
    components: {Head, Imge, Body, Footer},
    props: ["product"],
}
</script>
